# RFC003 single-entry action for decision->exec task flow.

# Goal
string type
int32 priority
string route_id
int32[] target_tags
ros_interfaces/Constraints constraints
int64 deadline_ms
builtin_interfaces/Time issue_time
---
# Result
string final_state
string error_code
string message
builtin_interfaces/Time finished_time
---
# Feedback
string state
float32 progress
int32 current_tag
int32 next_tag
string error_code
string message
builtin_interfaces/Time timestamp
